title: 'The Challenge: USA' Episode 5 | Surviving The Challenge
description:
Tyson Apostol and Amelia Wedemeyer break down the latest episode of 'The Challenge: USA.' They talk about Tyson's epic win this week, the Survivor contingent showing cracks, and who got eliminated this week.
Hosts: Tyson Apostol and Amelia Wedemeyer
Producer: Kaya McMullen
